snippet.textDisplay: Food for thought. Back in bible times to be cleared of sin and be right with God a person would take an animal to the high priest ( Who would stand as a physical representation of God ) to be sacrificed in their place because where there is sin death has to occur based on the Garden of eden, bite from the tree of knowledge and you will surely die. This is the reason why every one dies. To us death is natural but truth be told everyone lives forever and for man to live just to die was not the original arrangement. whenever a man took an animal to the high priest, the high priest never examined the sinner or asked questions like what sin did you commit. The only thing examined was the animal. This same event will take place in the spiritual when we stand before God and God in all His wisdom and Goodness is not going to examine a sinner looking for sin because there is not one person without sin but what He will examine is your animal and Jesus is the Lamb of God. You do not have to stop sinning, join a church and become part of a religion to be at peace with God because ALL the requirements demanded of us by the law or word of God were met and satisfied through the Life, Death and Resurrection of Jesus Christ in our place. What is impossible with man is possible with God. Jesus says IT IS FINISHED. Salvation or peace with God is a FREE gift, not a reward. God forgives ALL sin. Even a serial killer woke up this morning and guess Who woke him up? GOD. All it takes is a simple prayer of faith for WHOSOEVER calls upon the name of the Lord shall be saved. PRAYER OF FAITH - DEAR JESUS I ASK THAT YOU REMEMBER ME WHEN I STAND BEFORE YOU. AMEN.
